Detailed Description

Routines:

  • util_queue_create - Creates a new queue.
  • util_queue_async_insert - Inserts a new object into the queue.
  • util_queue_async_query - Extracts an object from the queue.
  • util_queue_sync_insert - Inserts a new object into the queue. Threadsafe variant by usage of a critical section.
  • util_queue_sync_query - Extracts an object from the queue. Threadsafe variant by usage of a critical section.
